#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:11
msgid "**⚙️ RONL Business API — v2.9.7** · *April 2026*"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:11
msgid "**AI Assistant — MCP providers & multi-model LLM registry**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:11
msgid ""
"AI Assistant extended with three independent MCP providers — CPRMV "
"legislation (Dutch & EU law), LDE Process Library (deployed BPMN bundles, "
"forms, document templates), and a multi-model LLM registry supporting both "
"Claude and GPT-4o. New Procesbibliotheek section on the Home tab lets "
"caseworkers browse deployed processes without login. IOU tab for Flevoland: "
"use-case submission with file attachments, feedback with screenshot upload, "
"and read-only GitLab issue lists."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:11
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:11"
