msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:31
msgid "**🔍 Linked Data Explorer — v1.6.0** · *April 2026*"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:31
msgid "**Multilingualism & pending-until-Save editing**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:31
msgid ""
"BPMN processes, Camunda forms, and document templates now carry an optional "
"[language and organization]{1} — set via the editor footer panel, persisted "
"to PostgreSQL and (for BPMN) to `ronl:language` / `ronl:organization` in the "
"XML. List panels gain a search box, a language filter, and collapsible "
"organization groups. The deploy modal warns inline when a bundle mixes "
"languages. Footer edits across all three editors now use a pending-until-"
"Save model with shell → subprocess atomic propagation. Ships with the Dutch "
"HR-capacity reference bundle (1 BPMN, 8 forms, 2 documents) demonstrating "
"stable English DMN keys with translated labels."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:31
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:31"
msgid "[:octicons-arrow-right-24: Full changelog]{1}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:41
msgid "**📜 CPRMV API — v0.4.0** · *February 2026*"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:41
msgid "**On-the-fly Rule Retrieval**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:41
msgid ""
"Live retrieval and CPRMV transformation of Dutch and EU legislation from "
"BWB, CVDR, and EU CELLAR repositories. Automatic latest-version resolution, "
"seven output formats, definition extraction with parse patterns, and "
"Juriconnect reference resolution."
msgstr ""

