#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:55
msgid "What is IOU Architecture?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:57
msgid ""
"The Information Architecture Framework for IOU integrates semantic web "
"technologies, decision models, and Dutch government standards into a unified "
"system for managing regulatory compliance and spatial planning."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/index.md:71
msgid "Architecture Overview"
msgstr ""

